N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 1.74 - Executive Order No. 74: Repealing and revoking the Executive Order dated April 2, 1971 [No. 49] relating to the Crime Control Planning Board and Office of Crime Control Planning

State Regulations

Executive Order Number 49, dated April 2, 1971, is hereby
repealed and revoked, effective September 1, 1972, the substantive provisions
of such order having been embodied in and superseded by chapter 399 of the Laws
of 1972 effective on the same date. Signed: Nelson A. Rockefeller

Dated: February 5, 1973
